<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ma khan Mosie'n Kanaan a thila,
 Luoh zolo in Lal thuthun a paw ie;
 Kanaan gam lopi leh a hawihna a mu'i,
 Kisika ngaiin kap in a maw !

[V2]
 Aw, ken le Kanaan thak chu ka thil ,
 Ka hatna suongin tung thei puong ka;
 Mahleh Lal Jehovin ei pui intin,
 Gam nuom zie bang lawm chu va mu tang ka,

[V3]
 2. Kanaan khawvui leh nitum kawl eng,
 Puipa Mosi chun a vak gal thila;
 Jordan galkaih chu Lal in a phal ta puoi,
 A hehpihte cheng a khen mai tai .

[V4]
 3. Lunghel um tang ka ngai na zen e,
 Lalna'n a kilawm ie kumsawt gam chu;
 Ziechun Zopa Belam No Lal a chu ie,
 A sika Lalna pakin a um.

[V5]
 4. Kanaan pakcha leh khawtang mawi chu,
 Puipa Mosi'n nungtieng a sawn ta ie;
 Ngailo guolin Salem tang a kal to tai,
 Israel chate ngai ina maw?</lyrics>
<title>Lal Jehovain Ei Puiin !</title>
<hymn_number>142</hymn_number>
</song>